title: Ron Carter on What Jazz Has Meant to Him
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Legendary jazz bassist Ron Carter shares his thoughts on the most valuable lessons he has learned in the course of his career  both in terms of his personal growth and the musical collaborations he has participated in.
